716
00:50:32,785 --> 00:50:34,285
Still, please get started.

717
00:50:34,285 --> 00:50:36,456
I will get you the materials you need.

718
00:50:36,456 --> 00:50:37,555
All right.

719
00:50:37,555 --> 00:50:38,981
Hey.

720
00:50:39,656 --> 00:50:42,825
